 allow‚ÜêCheckLicenseFile path
‚çù If G is a variable rather than a namespace a 1 is returned (no INI file rules)
‚çù If the INI file requires a check for a LICENSE file and such a file exists in the root of the project a 1 is returned.
‚çù If the INI file does not require such a check a 1 is returned as well.
‚çù Otherwise a 0 is returned.
 allow‚Üê1
 :If 9=‚éïnc 'G'
 :AndIf G.INI.Exist'CONFIG:MustHaveLicenseFile'
 :AndIf G.INI.Get'CONFIG:MustHaveLicenseFile'
     allow‚ÜêF.IsFile path,'/LICENSE'
 :EndIf
